# Didactic Resources
:res_biggs rdf:type guide:DidacticResource ; guide:bibliographyTitle "N. Biggs: Discrete Mathematics, 2nd ed." ; guide:bibliographyType "Bibliografía" .
:res_gross rdf:type guide:DidacticResource ; guide:bibliographyTitle "J. Gross, J. Yellen: Graph Theory and its Applications" ; guide:bibliographyType "Bibliografía" .
:res_rosen rdf:type guide:DidacticResource ; guide:bibliographyTitle "K. H. Rosen: Matemática Discreta y sus aplicaciones" ; guide:bibliographyType "Bibliografía" .
:res_caballero rdf:type guide:DidacticResource ; guide:bibliographyTitle "Matemática Discreta para Informáticos" ; guide:bibliographyType "Bibliografía" .
:res_lipschutz rdf:type guide:DidacticResource ; guide:bibliographyTitle "Lipschutz, S.: Matemática Discreta" ; guide:bibliographyType "Bibliografía" .
:res_vieites rdf:type guide:DidacticResource ; guide:bibliographyTitle "A. Vieites y más: Teoría de Grafos" ; guide:bibliographyType "Bibliografía" .
:res_agnarsson rdf:type guide:DidacticResource ; guide:bibliographyTitle "G. Agnarsson: Graph theory" ; guide:<0xC2>bibliographyType "Bibliografía" .
:res_balakrishnan rdf:type guide:DidacticResource ; guide:bibliographyTitle "V. K. Balakrishnan: Graph Theory" ; guide:bibliographyType "Bibliografía" .
:res_chartrand rdf:type guide:DidacticResource ; guide:bibliographyTitle "G. Chartrand, P. Zhang: Introduction to Graph Theory" ;guide:bibliographyType "Bibliografía" .
:res_kocay rdf:type guide:DidacticResource ; guide:bibliographyTitle "W. Kocay, D. Kreher: Graphs, Algorithms and Optimization" ; guide:bibliographyType "Bibliografía" .
:res_koh rdf:type guide:DidacticResource ; guide:bibliographyTitle "Koh Khee Meng et al.: Introduction to Graph Theory" ; guide:bibliographyType "Bibliografía" .
:res_marcus rdf:type guide:DidacticResource ; guide:bibliographyTitle "D. Marcus: Graph Theory, A Problem Oriented Approach" ; guide:bibliographyType "Bibliografía" .
:res_matousek rdf:type guide:DidacticResource ; guide:bibliographyTitle "J. Matousek, J. Nesetril: Invitación a la matemática discreta" ; guide:bibliographyType "Bibliografía" .
:res_west rdf:type guide:DidacticResource ; guide:bibliographyTitle "D. B. West: Introduction to Graph Theory" ; guide:bibliographyType "Bibliografía" .

